data.description: This charming home in the quaint neighborhood of Country Club Hills features a 1st Floor Office, Dining Room w/ French doors, and Family Room embellished with crown molding and brick fireplace. Eat-in Kitchen boasts a beautiful bay window, Granite counters, and tile backsplash. Head upstairs to find the Master Suite w/ updated shower and three spacious secondary bedrooms. Fenced yard, Irrigation Sys, new Deck, Patio, double driveway, convenient location, and so much more!
